*Predstava* je večeras počela u devet časova. (The performance started at nine o'clock tonight.)

*Predstavu* je izveo izvanredan glumac. (An outstanding actor performed the show.)

Mnogi ljudi su došli da vide *predstavu*. (Many people came to see the performance.)

*Predstavama* su se deca divili. (The children were amazed by the performances.)

On je posvetio celog života *predstavama*. (He devoted his life to performances.)